  "summary": "Apache Tomcat: Incomplete escaping of JSON access logs",
  "details": "Improper Encoding or Escaping of Output vulnerability in the JsonAccessLogValve component of Apache Tomcat.\n\nThis issue affects Apache Tomcat: from 11.0.0 through 11.0.20, from 10.1.0 through 10.1.53, from 9.0.40 through 9.0.116.\n\nUsers are recommended to upgrade to version 11.0.21, 10.1.54 or 9.0.117 , which fix the issue.",
